{"tid":1260553,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】特朗普：如無協議將對華加稅　或加稅10%","createTime":"2019-06-27T01:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T02:39:26.000Z","uid":66271,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f14c0d7817e3ad76726b356ba600b1942bbdb4d2","tid":1260553,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2961577/org/62102829193208c710aae83bb6e52ca3.jpg/difRAszGU-QRCECO6MZ6cGaPLvqRkJbgDWROkQ1kTpE?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2961577%2Forg%2F62102829193208c710aae83bb6e52ca3.jpg%2FdifRAszGU-QRCECO6MZ6cGaPLvqRkJbgDWROkQ1kTpE%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=003cff4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）周三（26日）接受媒體訪問時指，若然他無法與中國國家主席習近平達成貿易協議，他將再對中國商品加徵關稅。<br />\n他並提到，對下一階段採取不同策略抱持開放態度，下一輪若是加徵中國貨品關稅時，有可能是加徵10%關稅，而不是25%。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普當天接受霍士商業新聞（Fox Business）的訪問時指，他對關稅的看法與很多人都不相同。他稱，若然與中國未能達成協議，他已準備好再對其餘價值3500億美元的進口中國商品加徵關稅，但他提到下一階段也有可能使用不同的策略，即是加徵的關稅稅率可能是10%，而不是25%。<br />\n特朗普又認為「他們（中國）比我更想達成協議。」<br />\n目前美國對價值約2500億美元的進口中國貨品加徵25%關稅，特朗普之前也曾多次威脅向其餘的進口中國貨品加稅。"},{"pid":"d50d4bf781c01f7eb1107113a8af25890b2b9200","tid":1260553,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"97a7608d4a9d3a668de599b69dc62f92f98e7c9d","tid":1260553,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"又縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf0873f8b3440928f5772fa6933182d8af7f0a3","tid":1260553,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"97a7608d4a9d3a668de599b69dc62f92f98e7c9d","tid":1260553,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:09:39.000Z","msg":"又縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:12:14.000Z","msg":"好亂<img s